<p><strong>(15)</strong>	<strong>	Waters Generally Supporting Shellfish.</strong>  Waters designated by the Coastal Resources Division as productive shellfish waters
(currently producing or with the potential to produce shellfish) are opened and closed according to State Law and the requirements
of the National Shellfish Sanitation Program Manual of Operations.  For a current listing of open productive shellfish waters,
contact the Coastal Resources Division.  Specific water reaches generally supporting shellfish are as follows:

<br wp="br1"><br wp="br2">
<p><strong>CHATHAM COUNTY</strong>

<br wp="br1"><br wp="br2">
