<br wp="br1"><br wp="br2">
<p> 4.	Herb River at confluence with Wilmington River to County Road 890.

<br wp="br1"><br wp="br2">
<p> 5.	All waters surrounding Skidaway Island including Moon River North to Skidaway Island Road.

<br wp="br1"><br wp="br2">
<p> 6.	Vernon River at Vernonburg and eastward.

<br wp="br1"><br wp="br2">
<p> 7.	Little Ogeechee River from Rose Dhu Island and eastward excluding Harvey Creek on Harvey's Island.

<br wp="br1"><br wp="br2">
<p> 8.	Ogeechee River below Shad Island and eastward (north of center line).

