<p><strong>Authority</strong> Ga. L. 1964, p. 416, et seq., as amended (Ga. Code Ann.  17-501 et seq.); Ga. Laws 1972, p. 1015 et seq., as amended (Ga. Code Ann.  40-3501 et seq.); Ga. Laws 1964. p. 416 as amended (Ga
