<DOCHDR>
http://www.dnr.state.ga.us:80/lpb/lpbnar.htm 167.193.53.2 19970121114614 text/html 14791
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Tue, 21 Jan 1997 11:50:02 GMT
