<Title> CRD Administration Homepage</Title>    
<H1> Welcome to Adminstrative Services </H1>
<H2>Coastal Resources Division, Georgia Dept. of Natural Resources</H2>

<img src = art/color_swirl.gif ><p>


     The administrative functions of CRD are performed by the
Director, an Administrative
Secretary, an Administrative Services Manager II, a Receptionist,
a Support Services Coordinator,
and a Computer Network Coordinator.  CRD's Administration
performs the managerial,
supervisory, personnel, planning, computer services, and
maintenance functions for the Division
and serves as the principal link with the Commissioner's office
and department staff in Atlanta. 
In addition, this unit provides reception duties and
building/grounds maintenance, and basic
management duties for the Coastal Regional Headquarters office
complex.<p>

<A HREF = history.htm >CRD History</A><p>

<A HREF = computer.htm > Computer and Information Systems </A><p>

<A HREF = stats.htm >Cooperative Statistics Program </A></pre><p>

