<h1> Saltwater Gamefish Records Project </h1>

<h2> Outer Continental Shelf Program</h2>

<h3> Henry Ansley, Program Leader</h3>

<p><img src="art/blue_marble.gif"></p>

<p> </p>

<pre>

	The Saltwater Gamefish Records Project recognizes
landings of record sized fish (based on weight), and also
recognizes exceptional or unique marine angling experiences.
A Georgia Saltwater Gamefish Record Certificate is awarded for
entries exceeding or tying existing records in Men's and Women's
categories. An Outstanding Catch Certificate may be given for
a variety of entries encompassing all marine finfish and
exceptional, yet non-record, catches.
</pre>
<a href="records.htm">

<p>Current Records - Men's Division</a></p>

<p> <a href="women.htm">Current Records - Women's Division</a></p>

