double-lane ramp).</p>

<p> (10) Houlihan Boat Ramp Park: Take Exit 19 south on GA HWY 30
for 2.7 miles. Turn left and continue south on GA HWY 30 for an
additional 0.9 miles to GA HWY 25. Turn left (north) for 0.8
miles. Park located on right before crossing the Houlihan Bridge
(Savannah River). (Two double-lane ramps).</p>

<p> (11) Kings Ferry Community Park Boat Ramp: Take Exit 16 east
on GA HWY 204 for 2.1 miles to U.S. HWY 17. Take HWY 17 south for
2.7 miles. Park located on left before crossing Ogeechee River
