<h1> Guide to Fishing Access Sites </h1>

<p> </p>

<h2> Bryan County </h2>

<p><img src="art/blue_marble.gif"></p>

<p> DRIVING DIRECTIONS FROM INTERSTATE-95</p>

<p> <em>NON-BOATING FISHING SITES </em></p>

<p> (1) Fort McAllister Ogeechee River Pier: Take Exit 15 east on
GA HWY 144 for 6.6 miles to GA HWY SPUR 144. Turn left for 3.7
miles to Fort McAllister State Park. Visitors must check in at
Park office located on right approximately 0.1 mile past Park
entrance. Pier located 0.2 miles from Park office on left.</p>

<p> (2) Fort McAllister Red Bird Creek Dock: Take Exit 15 east on
GA HWY 144 for 6.6 miles to GA HWY SPUR 144. Turn left for 3.7
miles to Fort McAllister State Park. Visitors must check in at
Park office located on right approximately 0.1 mile past Park
entrance. Dock and camp grounds located 1.5 miles from Park
office. Dock access limited to Park campers only. Obtain
additional information at Park entrance office. </p>

<p> (3) Tivoli River Fishing Docks: Take Exit 15 east on GA HWY
144 for 10.1 miles to Belfast Road (look for forestry tower).
Turn right 1.9 miles to Tivoli River. </p>

<p> <em>BOAT RAMPS</em></p>

<p> (4) Demeries Creek Boat Ramp: Take Exit 15 east on GA HWY 144
for 14.1 miles. Ramp located on the right near the Georgia
Department of Natural Resources Law Enforcement Office. (One
single-lane ramp)</p>

<p> (5) Fort McAllister Ogeechee River Boat Ramp: Take Exit 15
east on GA HWY 144 for 6.6 miles to GA HWY SPUR 144. Turn left
3.7 miles to Fort McAllister State Park Entrance. Ramp located on
left before entering Fort McAllister State Park. (One single-lane
ramp)</p>

<p> (6) Fort McAllister Red Bird Creek Boat Ramp: Take Exit 15
east on GA HWY 144 for 6.6 miles to GA HWY SPUR 144. Turn left
3.7 miles to Fort McAllister State Park. Visitors must check in
at Park office located on right approximately 0.1 mile past Park
entrance. Boat ramp and camp grounds located 1.5 miles from Park
office. Boating access limited to Park campers only. Obtain
additional information at Park entrance office. (One single-lane
ramp)</p>

<p> <em>MARINAS</em></p>

<p> (7) Fort McAllister Marina: Take Exit 15 east on GA HWY 144
for 6.6 miles to GA HWY SPUR 144. Turn left 3.1 miles to Marina
located on left side of road. Facility provides hoist lift
launching (24,000 lb). Phone: (912) 727-2632</p>

<p> (8) Kilkenny Fish Camp: Take Exit 15 east on GA HWY 144 for
12.5 miles to Kilkenny Road. Turn left 2.9 miles until pavement
ends. Follow dirt road for 0.1 miles to fish camp. Facility
provides hoist lift launching (4,000 lb). Phone: (912) 727-2215</p>

