<h2><img src="http://www.dnr.state.ga.us/images/wrd.gif" align=left hspace=0 width=100 height=100>Wildlife ResourcesDivision</h2>
<p>&#160;The Wildlife Resources Division manages, protects, and encourages the wise use of all wildlife, fish and 
protected plants. The division operates recreation areas for hunting, fishing, and other wildlife-related 
recreation, and enforces laws regulating wildlife, boating and littering to ensure the protection of Georgia&#146;s 
natural resources. Through ongoing information and education programs, the division promotes conservation, sportsmanship, 
safety awareness, and encourages citizens to be responsible stewards of the environment.<br>
</p>
